---

<Mainlayouts>
  <section class="bongrid">
    <div class="indextext">
      <p>The theme for UX Copenhagen 2024 is:</p>
      <h1>DEGROWTH & CONSUMERISM</h1>
      <h2 class="indexh2">CONFERENCE 20-21 MARCH 2024</h2>
      <Button ButtonTitle="TICKETS" ButtonLink="/tickets" />
    </div>
    <img class="fakebon" src="/img/bong_kort.svg" alt="bon" />
  </section>
  <div class="øverst">
    <img src="/logo_stort.svg" alt="logo" />
  </div>
  <section class="videobox">
    <video width="100%" controls autoplay loop>
      <source src="../mov/uxfeel.webm" type="video/webm" />
       Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>
    <h2 class="text">THAT UX COPENHAGEN FEEL</h2>
  </section>
  <h2 class="speakers_t">FEATURED SPEAKERS</h2>
  <section class="speakers">
    {
      data.map((speaker) => {
        return <Speakers data={speaker} />;
      })
    }
  </section>
  <section class="grid1_1">
    <div>
      <img class="img_str" src="/img/ux_scene.webp" alt="ux scene" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="farve str">WHAT TO EXPECT</h2>
      <p class="farve">
        Welcome to the UX Copenhagen conference – Denmark’s most inspirational
        human experience conference, covering subjects like user experience,
        content, strategy, and research under a new theme for each year. We will
        present you with two days filled with superb content from 20+ local and
        international speakers, hands-on workshops, inspiration, networking, new
        knowledge, and new insights. <br /><br /> Our speakers and participants
        are a fantastic mixture of international and local Danish UX experts,
        marketing professionals, digital managers, designers, innovators,
        strategists, researchers, and others interested in the field. The
        conference is run by Helle Martens’ tiny indie business team, and fueled
        by a strong passion for the field of UX and design.
      </p>
      <a class="read" href="/about">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Mainlayouts>

<style>
  /* MOBIL*/
  h2 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .str {
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .speakers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .grid1_1 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    background-color: #284d3b;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .bongrid {
    display: flex;
    margin-left: 5%;
    margin-right: 5%;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .fakebon {
    width: 50%;
    margin-left: 49%;
    margin-top: -12%;
    order: 0;
  }
  .indexh2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: lighter;
    margin-top: 0px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
  }
  .indextext {
    margin-top: 5%;
    margin-left: -10%;
  }
  .videobox {
    background-color: #ffe7e9;
    padding-top: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .text {
    text-align: end;
    margin: 10px;
    color: #284d3b;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .farve {
    color: #ffe7e9;
    margin: 20px;
    margin-right: 22px;
  }
  .øverst {
    margin-top: -17%;
  }
  .speakers {
    margin-bottom: 10%;
  }
  .speakers_t {
    margin-top: 10%;
  }
  .read {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #ffe7e9;
    margin-left: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  /* DESKTOP */
  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .speakers {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    video {
      object-fit: cover;
      align-self: stretch;
      height: 450px;
    }
    .grid1_1 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      background-color: #284d3b;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      margin-left: -10%;
      margin-right: -10%;
    }
    /* .img_str{
    margin: 25px;
  } */
    .videobox {
      margin-left: -10%;
      margin-right: -10%;
      background-color: #ffe7e9;
      padding-top: 80px;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .øverst {
      margin-left: -5%;
      margin-right: -5%;
    }
    .text {
      text-align: end;
      margin: 20px;
      color: #284d3b;
      font-size: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
